Class PathList

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.PathList

  • public class PathList
extends Object
    Static class containing paths to files required by the generator.

      • TRAINING_DIR

        public static final String TRAINING_DIR
        path to the directory which contains all AMR graphs used for training. Note that these AMR graphs are not to be stored directly in the TRAINING_DIR, but instead inside the subdirectories specified by AMR_SUBDIRECTORIES.

      • POS_FILENAME

        public static final String POS_FILENAME
        the names of the files which contain the POS tags corresponding to the reference realizations of the AMR graphs stored in file AMR_FILENAME. Each subdirectory (see AMR_SUBDIRECTORIES) must contain a file with this name if the AMR graphs are to be used for training.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
